{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2019-12-17-firebase-deploy/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"박준우 블로그"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"0636fb02-1ad8-57ef-9c0f-1c60e0a9183b","excerpt":"저는 프로젝트를 완성시킨 다음, 배포를 진행해야 한다는 생각을 가지고 있었습니다. 그래서 배포한 프로젝트가 없.. localhost에서 늘 혼자만 보다가 어느샌가 사라져버리는건 이젠 더이상은 naver.. 누군가가 호스팅 URL…","html":"<p>저는 프로젝트를 완성시킨 다음, 배포를 진행해야 한다는 생각을 가지고 있었습니다.</p>\n<p><del>그래서 배포한 프로젝트가 없..</del></p>\n<p>localhost에서 늘 혼자만 보다가 어느샌가 사라져버리는건 이젠 더이상은 naver..</p>\n<p>누군가가 호스팅 URL을 통해 보고있으면 더 재미있으니깐, 정말 아무것도 없이 네비게이션 바 라우팅만 되어있는 프로젝트라고해도 앞으로는 배포를 먼저 해버리고 프로젝트를 시작하려고 Firebase Cloud Hosting을 시도해보고 기록으로 남깁니다.</p>\n<br>\n<h2>Step 1. Firebase CLI 설치</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">npm install -g firebase-tools</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/50ef952dbc19bbd3019c5ea0d4cd16d9/ccf0c/firebase_deploy1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 19.62025316455696%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"deploy1\"\n        title=\"deploy1\"\n        src=\"/static/50ef952dbc19bbd3019c5ea0d4cd16d9/f058b/firebase_deploy1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/50ef952dbc19bbd3019c5ea0d4cd16d9/c26ae/firebase_deploy1.png 158w,\n/static/50ef952dbc19bbd3019c5ea0d4cd16d9/6bdcf/firebase_deploy1.png 315w,\n/static/50ef952dbc19bbd3019c5ea0d4cd16d9/f058b/firebase_deploy1.png 630w,\n/static/50ef952dbc19bbd3019c5ea0d4cd16d9/40601/firebase_deploy1.png 945w,\n/static/50ef952dbc19bbd3019c5ea0d4cd16d9/78612/firebase_deploy1.png 1260w,\n/static/50ef952dbc19bbd3019c5ea0d4cd16d9/ccf0c/firebase_deploy1.png 1428w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n<hr>\n<h2>Step 2. Firebase CLI를 사용하여 로그인</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">firebase login</code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">firebase login</code> 명령어로 로컬머신을 Firebase에 연결하고, Firebase 프로젝트에대한 액세스 권한을 부여받을 수 있습니다.</p>\n<br>\n<hr>\n<h2>Step 3. 액세스 확인</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">firebase list //해당 명령어는 deprecated되었네요. 아래 명령어를 입력해주세요.\nfirebase projects:list</code></pre></div>\n<p><a href=\"https://console.firebase.google.com/u/0/\">Firebase Console</a> 에 추가해둔 프로젝트들이 터미널창에 나열되면 제대로 액세스 된 것입니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ef383a20542bd23b0c8fc69d5c809d52/c4451/firebase_deploy2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 34.810126582278485%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"deploy2\"\n        title=\"deploy2\"\n        src=\"/static/ef383a20542bd23b0c8fc69d5c809d52/f058b/firebase_deploy2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ef383a20542bd23b0c8fc69d5c809d52/c26ae/firebase_deploy2.png 158w,\n/static/ef383a20542bd23b0c8fc69d5c809d52/6bdcf/firebase_deploy2.png 315w,\n/static/ef383a20542bd23b0c8fc69d5c809d52/f058b/firebase_deploy2.png 630w,\n/static/ef383a20542bd23b0c8fc69d5c809d52/40601/firebase_deploy2.png 945w,\n/static/ef383a20542bd23b0c8fc69d5c809d52/78612/firebase_deploy2.png 1260w,\n/static/ef383a20542bd23b0c8fc69d5c809d52/c4451/firebase_deploy2.png 1450w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>한 번 <a href=\"https://console.firebase.google.com/u/0/\">Firebase Console 링크</a>로 들어가서 테스트해보겠습니다.</p>\n<p>링크에 접속하면 그동안 생성했던 프로젝트들과 <code class=\"language-text\">프로젝트 추가</code> 버튼이 있습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b3b2b4af5b35456503517771e822f3d4/5f78c/firebase_deploy4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 96.20253164556962%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"deploy4\"\n        title=\"deploy4\"\n        src=\"/static/b3b2b4af5b35456503517771e822f3d4/f058b/firebase_deploy4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b3b2b4af5b35456503517771e822f3d4/c26ae/firebase_deploy4.png 158w,\n/static/b3b2b4af5b35456503517771e822f3d4/6bdcf/firebase_deploy4.png 315w,\n/static/b3b2b4af5b35456503517771e822f3d4/f058b/firebase_deploy4.png 630w,\n/static/b3b2b4af5b35456503517771e822f3d4/40601/firebase_deploy4.png 945w,\n/static/b3b2b4af5b35456503517771e822f3d4/78612/firebase_deploy4.png 1260w,\n/static/b3b2b4af5b35456503517771e822f3d4/5f78c/firebase_deploy4.png 1606w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>버튼을 눌러주면 이제 프로젝트 만들기 단계가 시작되는데요.</p>\n<p>프로젝트 이름을 채워줍니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/937fe777cb82610559de8fecbd57c9cb/07d7d/firebase_deploy5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 86.70886075949367%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"deploy5\"\n        title=\"deploy5\"\n        src=\"/static/937fe777cb82610559de8fecbd57c9cb/f058b/firebase_deploy5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/937fe777cb82610559de8fecbd57c9cb/c26ae/firebase_deploy5.png 158w,\n/static/937fe777cb82610559de8fecbd57c9cb/6bdcf/firebase_deploy5.png 315w,\n/static/937fe777cb82610559de8fecbd57c9cb/f058b/firebase_deploy5.png 630w,\n/static/937fe777cb82610559de8fecbd57c9cb/40601/firebase_deploy5.png 945w,\n/static/937fe777cb82610559de8fecbd57c9cb/78612/firebase_deploy5.png 1260w,\n/static/937fe777cb82610559de8fecbd57c9cb/07d7d/firebase_deploy5.png 1478w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>이 다음은 GA 설정인데요.</p>\n<p>저는 필요가 없어서 꺼버렸습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/90fe6273b77ac06e0f6f564ed2f08a7f/df438/firebase_deploy6.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 96.83544303797468%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"deploy6\"\n        title=\"deploy6\"\n        src=\"/static/90fe6273b77ac06e0f6f564ed2f08a7f/f058b/firebase_deploy6.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/90fe6273b77ac06e0f6f564ed2f08a7f/c26ae/firebase_deploy6.png 158w,\n/static/90fe6273b77ac06e0f6f564ed2f08a7f/6bdcf/firebase_deploy6.png 315w,\n/static/90fe6273b77ac06e0f6f564ed2f08a7f/f058b/firebase_deploy6.png 630w,\n/static/90fe6273b77ac06e0f6f564ed2f08a7f/40601/firebase_deploy6.png 945w,\n/static/90fe6273b77ac06e0f6f564ed2f08a7f/78612/firebase_deploy6.png 1260w,\n/static/90fe6273b77ac06e0f6f564ed2f08a7f/df438/firebase_deploy6.png 1556w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>프로젝트 만들기버튼을 누르면, 이제 프로젝트가 생성됩니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e06c3772b0b67d44f17a6c0eb11994f2/891d5/firebase_deploy7.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 102.53164556962024%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAVCAIAAADJt1n/AAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAgUlEQVQ4y+3SvQ7CMAwE4L7/zMSTsRWoAhKo/DQ+x3ETmfQNcKcOlW79fNLJHae8Ot2Ot4RlDSbIklTdGMwQK/GUr0di9eEYoXMxKxYO9O6x9Mu/mJAkq5nVWgiAqzmJhtu9P1+GIUyxXVLfYN+JHs9xfH3A4l67tUmeW/bf3gj+Ad94v59qRrxBAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"deploy7\"\n        title=\"deploy7\"\n        src=\"/static/e06c3772b0b67d44f17a6c0eb11994f2/f058b/firebase_deploy7.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e06c3772b0b67d44f17a6c0eb11994f2/c26ae/firebase_deploy7.png 158w,\n/static/e06c3772b0b67d44f17a6c0eb11994f2/6bdcf/firebase_deploy7.png 315w,\n/static/e06c3772b0b67d44f17a6c0eb11994f2/f058b/firebase_deploy7.png 630w,\n/static/e06c3772b0b67d44f17a6c0eb11994f2/40601/firebase_deploy7.png 945w,\n/static/e06c3772b0b67d44f17a6c0eb11994f2/78612/firebase_deploy7.png 1260w,\n/static/e06c3772b0b67d44f17a6c0eb11994f2/891d5/firebase_deploy7.png 1520w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>생성이 완료되었으면, 다시 터미널로 돌아가서 <code class=\"language-text\">firebase list</code> 명령어를 입력해서 확인해봅니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8780841a246fbc8a1d0710f996147d7f/66632/firebase_deploy8.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 29.11392405063291%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"deploy8\"\n        title=\"deploy8\"\n        src=\"/static/8780841a246fbc8a1d0710f996147d7f/f058b/firebase_deploy8.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8780841a246fbc8a1d0710f996147d7f/c26ae/firebase_deploy8.png 158w,\n/static/8780841a246fbc8a1d0710f996147d7f/6bdcf/firebase_deploy8.png 315w,\n/static/8780841a246fbc8a1d0710f996147d7f/f058b/firebase_deploy8.png 630w,\n/static/8780841a246fbc8a1d0710f996147d7f/40601/firebase_deploy8.png 945w,\n/static/8780841a246fbc8a1d0710f996147d7f/78612/firebase_deploy8.png 1260w,\n/static/8780841a246fbc8a1d0710f996147d7f/66632/firebase_deploy8.png 1504w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>생성한 프로젝트가 잘 보이네요!</p>\n<br>\n<hr>\n<h2>Step 4. 프로젝트 초기화</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">firebase init</code></pre></div>\n<p>배포작업에는 프로젝트 디렉터리 설정이 필요한데, <code class=\"language-text\">firebase init</code> 명령어가 바로 그 설정 단계입니다.</p>\n<p>명령어를 입력하면 터미널에 몇가지 질문들이 표시됩니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/524d5ae777bf8bc66ceebb86699c5644/3a4f1/firebase_deploy3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 22.151898734177216%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAECAIAAAABPYjBAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAhElEQVQI14XNWw6DIBQEUNZipTzKQwotj4KKSGT/KyofjZ82OZncj5lcICRcNlWPV21mP0xtujSY95s24x0NCF8BQkDncIxoWXEpJGfiPY5pnNTwfyyfzEfvgtXWGGf0W0+Kc0GFJCcufgfjiEr66MkR4xgoLecc0xo+s+9Csr10/fD0Bdg5KpLHA4wSAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"deploy3\"\n        title=\"deploy3\"\n        src=\"/static/524d5ae777bf8bc66ceebb86699c5644/f058b/firebase_deploy3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/524d5ae777bf8bc66ceebb86699c5644/c26ae/firebase_deploy3.png 158w,\n/static/524d5ae777bf8bc66ceebb86699c5644/6bdcf/firebase_deploy3.png 315w,\n/static/524d5ae777bf8bc66ceebb86699c5644/f058b/firebase_deploy3.png 630w,\n/static/524d5ae777bf8bc66ceebb86699c5644/40601/firebase_deploy3.png 945w,\n/static/524d5ae777bf8bc66ceebb86699c5644/78612/firebase_deploy3.png 1260w,\n/static/524d5ae777bf8bc66ceebb86699c5644/3a4f1/firebase_deploy3.png 2588w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>스페이스바를 눌러서 선택이 가능하고, 엔터키를 눌러서 다음 단계로 넘어갈 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p>저는, 호스팅만 필요하기때문에 호스팅만 선택한 뒤 넘어갑니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d23e6ebe69339ed462e3a725cb7572a4/820f7/firebase_deploy9.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 19.62025316455696%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAECAIAAAABPYjBAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAc0lEQVQI143MbQrDIAwGYI9itxm19asdTKO1vf+tGqwMf43BQ3iTkLB6YKkJ91hqzPuHakzbuhkS1mXkw+xDD1I9CCtnxoqkhZQP9G+n9BOAg5xuArhorYA+6cfWaWMlsU4tBoxTlPX8ute/se/70T+X5AJ15Cf1nyHhzQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"