static/756106ca991b78809d15133e56188eed/f058b/firebase_deploy10.png 630w,\n/static/756106ca991b78809d15133e56188eed/40601/firebase_deploy10.png 945w,\n/static/756106ca991b78809d15133e56188eed/97bfd/firebase_deploy10.png 1078w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>그리고 아까 만들었던 프로젝트를 선택해줍니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/654ca86d01ad2265f30b6f501d70354e/8740f/firebase_deploy11.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 24.68354430379747%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"deploy11\"\n        title=\"deploy11\"\n        src=\"/static/654ca86d01ad2265f30b6f501d70354e/f058b/firebase_deploy11.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/654ca86d01ad2265f30b6f501d70354e/c26ae/firebase_deploy11.png 158w,\n/static/654ca86d01ad2265f30b6f501d70354e/6bdcf/firebase_deploy11.png 315w,\n/static/654ca86d01ad2265f30b6f501d70354e/f058b/firebase_deploy11.png 630w,\n/static/654ca86d01ad2265f30b6f501d70354e/40601/firebase_deploy11.png 945w,\n/static/654ca86d01ad2265f30b6f501d70354e/8740f/firebase_deploy11.png 1106w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n<hr>\n<p>이제 Hosting 설정 단계입니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d89fb3f727aabf69ff14d0d3d7164d00/8cdda/firebase_deploy12.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 19.62025316455696%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"deploy12\"\n        title=\"deploy12\"\n        src=\"/static/d89fb3f727aabf69ff14d0d3d7164d00/f058b/firebase_deploy12.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d89fb3f727aabf69ff14d0d3d7164d00/c26ae/firebase_deploy12.png 158w,\n/static/d89fb3f727aabf69ff14d0d3d7164d00/6bdcf/firebase_deploy12.png 315w,\n/static/d89fb3f727aabf69ff14d0d3d7164d00/f058b/firebase_deploy12.png 630w,\n/static/d89fb3f727aabf69ff14d0d3d7164d00/40601/firebase_deploy12.png 945w,\n/static/d89fb3f727aabf69ff14d0d3d7164d00/8cdda/firebase_deploy12.png 1168w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>build 결과물의 디렉토리를 적어주면 됩니다.</p>\n<p>보통 Angular에서 <code class=\"language-text\">ng build</code> 명령어를 사용하면 따로 설정을 하지 않은 경우에는 dist/PROJECT_NAME 구조로 생성됩니다.</p>\n<p>저같은 경우에는 이렇게 dist 폴더 아래의 angular8-firebase-demo 폴더 아래에 index.html이 자리잡고 있습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b02737fe2543be755eb412d3720003cd/f941f/firebase_deploy13.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 102.53164556962024%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"deploy13\"\n        title=\"deploy13\"\n        src=\"/static/b02737fe2543be755eb412d3720003cd/f058b/firebase_deploy13.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b02737fe2543be755eb412d3720003cd/c26ae/firebase_deploy13.png 158w,\n/static/b02737fe2543be755eb412d3720003cd/6bdcf/firebase_deploy13.png 315w,\n/static/b02737fe2543be755eb412d3720003cd/f058b/firebase_deploy13.png 630w,\n/static/b02737fe2543be755eb412d3720003cd/f941f/firebase_deploy13.png 736w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>첫번째 질문에는 <code class=\"language-text\">dist/angular8-firebase-demo</code> 를 적어주고 나머지 질문에는 모두 <code class=\"language-text\">No</code> 를 선택해줍니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2f5b7aa47614dd999c4e2fe53fe92091/393aa/firebase_deploy14.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 24.68354430379747%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"deploy14\"\n        title=\"deploy14\"\n        src=\"/static/2f5b7aa47614dd999c4e2fe53fe92091/f058b/firebase_deploy14.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2f5b7aa47614dd999c4e2fe53fe92091/c26ae/firebase_deploy14.png 158w,\n/static/2f5b7aa47614dd999c4e2fe53fe92091/6bdcf/firebase_deploy14.png 315w,\n/static/2f5b7aa47614dd999c4e2fe53fe92091/f058b/firebase_deploy14.png 630w,\n/static/2f5b7aa47614dd999c4e2fe53fe92091/40601/firebase_deploy14.png 945w,\n/static/2f5b7aa47614dd999c4e2fe53fe92091/393aa/firebase_deploy14.png 1190w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Firebase initialization complete!</p>\n<br>\n<hr>\n<h2>Step5. 배포하기</h2>\n<br>\n<p>혹시 아직 <code class=\"language-text\">ng build --prod</code> 명령어로 빌드하지않았다면, 빌드를 먼저 진행해주세요.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">ng build --prod</code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<p>빌드가 완료되었으면 <code class=\"language-text\">firebase deploy</code> 명령어를 실행하여 배포를 시작합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">firebase deploy</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/77d8193ab097901fe5172f0bc8322448/081d5/firebase_deploy15.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 38.60759493670886%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"deploy15\"\n        title=\"deploy15\"\n        src=\"/static/77d8193ab097901fe5172f0bc8322448/f058b/firebase_deploy15.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/77d8193ab097901fe5172f0bc8322448/c26ae/firebase_deploy15.png 158w,\n/static/77d8193ab097901fe5172f0bc8322448/6bdcf/firebase_deploy15.png 315w,\n/static/77d8193ab097901fe5172f0bc8322448/f058b/firebase_deploy15.png 630w,\n/static/77d8193ab097901fe5172f0bc8322448/40601/firebase_deploy15.png 945w,\n/static/77d8193ab097901fe5172f0bc8322448/78612/firebase_deploy15.png 1260w,\n/static/77d8193ab097901fe5172f0bc8322448/081d5/firebase_deploy15.png 1264w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n<p>배포가 성공적으로 완료되면, Hosting URL에 들어가서 잘 동작하는지 확인해보면 됩니다!</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Firebase CLI를 사용하여 배포하기","date":"December 17, 2019","description":"저는 프로젝트를 완성시킨 다음, 배포를 진행해야 한다는 생각을 가지고 있었습니다."}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2019-11-04-memory-model/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"<번역>자바스크립트의 메모리 모델"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2020-01-14-observable-creation/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"옵저버블 생성함수"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"0636fb02-1ad8-57ef-9c0f-1c60e0a9183b","previousPostId":"46bfd331-ded2-5df7-b67b-4999ddc67d8f","nextPostId":"d3c11149-2d79-56b4-9260-8c588d7cce52"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","916993862"]}